org.magnos.asset.source

Packages that use org.magnos.asset.source
org.magnos.asset.source   
 

Classes in org.magnos.asset.source used by org.magnos.asset.source
DatabaseSource
          A source that reads assets from a database connection.
FileSource
          A source that reads assets from the file-system.
FtpSource
          A source that reads assets from an FTP server.
JarSource
          A source that reads assets from a JAR file.
MulticastSource
          A source that reads assets from a multicast group.
SmartSource.PatternedSource
          A simple class holding a regular expression pattern, the accompanying AssetSource, and the group in the pattern to use to determine the true request for the source.
SslSource
          A source that sends the request to a server over SSL and the server returns the asset requested.
TcpSource
          A source that sends the request to a server over TCP and the server returns the asset requested.
UdpSource
          A source that reads assets from a UDP server.
WebSource
          A source that reads assets from a web URL (currently only HTTP tested).
